com.captiveimagination.jgn
Class MessageQueue

java.lang.Object
  com.captiveimagination.jgn.MessageQueue

public class MessageQueue
extends java.lang.Object

MessageQueue receives all incoming messages from the server and processes them and calls the MessageListeners accordingly. This queue is instantiated directly in MessageServer and need not be instantiated by implementers of the API.

Author:
Matthew D. Hicks
